item.title: CVE-2020-4651|2024-09-17T03:27:35.881Z -- ibm -- maximo%20spatial%20asset%20management
item.description: IBM Maximo Spatial Asset Management 7.6.0.3, 7.6.0.4, 7.6.0.5, and 7.6.1.0 is vulnerable to cross-site request forgery which could allow an attacker to execute malicious and unauthorized actions transmitted from a user that the website trusts. IBM X-Force ID: 186024.

item.title: CVE-2020-4650|2024-09-17T02:32:29.659Z -- ibm -- maximo%20spatial%20asset%20management
item.description: IBM Maximo Spatial Asset Management 7.6.0.3, 7.6.0.4, 7.6.0.5, and 7.6.1.0 allows web pages to be stored locally which can be read by another user on the system. IBM X-Force ID: 186023.
